name: id
description: The text-based model id/name, also used to find the model on the website or in the API.

name: type
description: The model type, one of pretrained, fine-tuned, instruction-tuned, RL-tuned, or ?.

name: precision
description: The model precision.

name: params
description: Total model parameters (in billions).

name: average
description: Average model performance across the four metrics.

name: IFEval
description: Model performance on IFEval metric.

name: IFEval_Raw
description: Model performance on IFEval Raw metric.

name: MATH_Lvl_5
description: Model performance on MATH Lvl 5 metric.

name: MATH_Lvl_5_Raw
description: Model performance on MATH Lvl 5 Raw metric.

name: GPQA
description: Model performance on GPQA metric.

name: GPQA_Raw
description: Model performance on GPQA Raw metric.

name: MUSR
description: Model performance on MUSR metric.

name: MUSR_Raw
description: Model performance on MUSR Raw metric.

name: MMLU-PRO
description: Model performance on MMLU-PRO metric.

name: MMLU-PRO_Raw
description: Model performance on MMLU-PRO Raw metric.

name: submission_date
description: Submission date.

name: upload_to_hub_date
description: Upload to hub date.

name: hub
description: Model hub.

name: hub_license
description: Model hub license.

name: architecture
description: Model architecture.

name: model_website
description: Hugging Face website of model.

name: weight_type
description: Model weight type (e.g. Original, Adapter, Delta).

name: type_indicator
description: Visual symbol used to indicate type on model hub. This corresponds to the type field.

name: available_on_hub
description: Whether the model is available on the hub.

name: flagged
description: Whether the model has been flagged for unfair performance on the leaderboard.

name: not_merged
description: Whether the model has *not* been merged or fused.

name: mixture_of_experts
description: Whether the model is a Mixture of Experts (MoE) model.

name: chat_template
description: Whether the model is a chat template model.

name: generation
description: What generation the model is.

name: base_model
description: What base model the model is derived from.

name: maintainers_highlight
description: Whether the model is a maintainer's highlight.

name: sha
description: Model sha hash.
